{% comment %}
  GWP Auto-Add block
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  Install: Online Store → Themes → Customize → add this block anywhere
  in your theme layout (e.g. body / footer).

  NO settings to configure here.

  The gift product and minimum spend are read automatically from the
  product metafield (gwp.min_spend) set on your gift product in
  Shopify Admin → Products → [gift product] → Metafields.

  One-time product setup:
    1. Go to Shopify Admin → Products → [your gift product]
    2. Scroll to Metafields
    3. Set "GWP Minimum Spend" to e.g. 499
    4. Also add the tag  gwp-gift  to the product
    5. Save — auto-add will work on every storefront page.
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
{% endcomment %}

<script>
  window.__SHOP_DOMAIN__ = {{ shop.permanent_domain | json }};
</script>
<script src="{{ 'gwp-auto-add.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
{% schema %}
{
  "name": "GWP Auto Add",
  "target": "body",
  "javascript": "gwp-auto-add.js",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
